-### 5.3 Code-Split Boundaries
-
-React.lazy + dynamic import at the **screen level**:
-- `DashboardScreen` вЂ” in main bundle (critical path)
-- `SearchScreen` вЂ” lazy loaded (user navigates to search)
-- `DocumentScreen` вЂ” lazy loaded
-- `ActionSheet` вЂ” lazy loaded
-
-Shared UI components are in the main bundle (small, reused everywhere).
